message: Hi Bob! I have a product that I believe you'll find very valuable. I'm offering it to you for $14,000. It's a great deal considering its worth. Let me know if you're interested!
Thanks for the offer, Antony!  I'm really interested in the product, but $14000 is a bit above my budget.  Would you be willing to do $12500?  That's the highest I can go at this time.
